  Description : Me: Made a pizza tonight.  Voice sounds like: I'll bet.   Then at second 5 you can hear some say "pizza" in a lower voice.  Then immediately after I ask, "You guys like pizza?" And I immediately hear a distorted, harmonic "everybody" (assuming they mean "everybody likes pizza") then at second 8 I hear a harmonic "I'll bet you did"  The only very clear part is the first "I'll bet" but if you listen a bit more closer the other things can be heard too.
